Adult male.description: Black-and-white Warblers have a streakier back than Black-throated Gray Warblers. Also note that ranges rarely overlap on the breeding grounds.

Adult female.description: Black-and-white Warblers have a streakier back than Black-throated Gray Warblers. Ranges rarely overlap on the breeding grounds.

Breeding male.description: Blackpoll Warblers have a black crown and white cheek unlike the striped face of Black-throated Gray Warblers. Breeding ranges do not overlap.
